  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《无法抗拒的他们》中，你将化身为当代小镇女孩“夏言”，从一个小助理做起，突破各种困难，一步步成长为一个合格经纪人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这里，你可以与五个性格各异的成员进行互动，完成工作上的任务，体验不同的生活，在工作和爱情的抉择中，体悟不同人生的酸甜苦辣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >谁，才是你真爱的方向？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是自信果断，但又不失细腻敏感的门面主唱？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029880/extras/aaf3fce4a9c1aa274a53951d5c5948b4.avif?t=1733990484\" width=480 height=270 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是冷静沉稳，温柔且善解人意的海归队长？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029880/extras/5fca0c7eab4818dc052122f846684c10.avif?t=1733990484\" width=480 height=270 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是看似浪荡不羁，实则渴望被爱的说唱担当？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029880/extras/b06bd7cd46f77f35382a8f6a02290392.avif?t=1733990484\" width=480 height=270 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >又或是单纯天真，如同天使一般的主舞忙内？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029880/extras/ceb90bc31a7de78688ab65ca20d5cc33.avif?t=1733990484\" width=480 height=270 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还是外表英朗帅气，男友力十足的全能ACE？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029880/extras/a990d30727eab1260eb2394d24f89a58.avif?t=1733990484\" width=480 height=270 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >即刻入住“偶像之家”，做出你的选择！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>产品特色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-全程第一视角，沉浸式体验心动的感觉，让你体验真实生活中的情感起伏与抉择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-多个分支与结局，人生自在你手。无论是哪种结局，你都将通过自己不懈的努力，获得相应的成长与成绩。在这过程中可能经历了各种的挫折与挑战，但是只要有积极向上、敢于努力的决心与行动力，就会领略到人生不同的风景线。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-真人出演，实景互动。多和其他角色和所处的世界进行互动，或许会有惊喜发生噢！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >关注我们：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >QQ群：80893212</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >TapTap：无法抗拒的他们</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >抖音：网剧无法抗拒的他们</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >微信视频号：无法抗拒的他们</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《无法抗拒的他们》中，你将化身为当代小镇女孩“夏言”，从一个小助理做起，突破各种困难，一步步成长为一个合格经纪人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这里，你可以与五个性格各异的成员进行互动，完成工作上的任务，体验不同的生活，在工作和爱情的抉择中，体悟不同人生的酸甜苦辣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >谁，才是你真爱的方向？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是自信果断，但又不失细腻敏感的门面主唱？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029880/extras/aaf3fce4a9c1aa274a53951d5c5948b4.avif?t=1733990484\" width=480 height=270 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是冷静沉稳，温柔且善解人意的海归队长？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029880/extras/5fca0c7eab4818dc052122f846684c10.avif?t=1733990484\" width=480 height=270 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是看似浪荡不羁，实则渴望被爱的说唱担当？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029880/extras/b06bd7cd46f77f35382a8f6a02290392.avif?t=1733990484\" width=480 height=270 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >又或是单纯天真，如同天使一般的主舞忙内？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029880/extras/ceb90bc31a7de78688ab65ca20d5cc33.avif?t=1733990484\" width=480 height=270 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还是外表英朗帅气，男友力十足的全能ACE？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029880/extras/a990d30727eab1260eb2394d24f89a58.avif?t=1733990484\" width=480 height=270 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_p